        "body": "I agree that it would be good to explore this.  I do think that we should introduce it gradually with a configuration option.  I would be pleased to see that it was always preferred.  Regardless, the first thing to do here is probably to start introducing this functionality to many of the more commonly used collection creation routines like `dd.read_csv`, `dd.read_parquet`, and so on.\r\n\r\nI think that Xarray started doing this with dataset creation.  @jhamman may be able to say a bit about their experience.",
